      "results": [
        {
          "message": {
            "markdown": "The application's\u00a0**code_execution** method receives and\u00a0dynamically executes user-controlled code using\u00a0**exec**,\u00a0at line **76** of **/badguys/vulnerable/views.py**. This could enable an attacker to inject and run arbitrary code.\n\nThe attacker can inject the executed code via user input,\u00a0**POST**, which is retrieved by the application in the **code_execution** method, at line **68** of **/badguys/vulnerable/views.py**.\n\n",
            "text": "The application's\u00a0code_execution method receives and\u00a0dynamically executes user-controlled code using\u00a0exec,\u00a0at line 76 of /badguys/vulnerable/views.py. This could enable an attacker to inject and run arbitrary code.\n\nThe attacker can inject the executed code via user input,\u00a0POST, which is retrieved by the application in the code_execution method, at line 68 of /badguys/vulnerable/views.py.\n\n"
          },
          "locations": [
